title: Willie Nelson - Both Sides Now (1970) MP3@320
description:
Both Sides Now is a 1970 album by country singer Willie Nelson.

The title track aside, this is a pretty good album. While there aren't as many originals on this record as some of his albums released around this time, he manages to get something new out of several of his covers. Listening to "Everybody's Talkin'," you don't find youself longing for Nilsson's version. Similarly, after Jerry Lee ripped up "One Has My Name," Nelson still makes it sound fresh.

/Allmusic
